# Comments for future developers
# ==============================
# This .gitignore covers:
# - Python/Flask backend with SQLite database
# - React frontend with npm/yarn
# - Development tools and editors
# - Operating system files
# - Security-sensitive files
# - Build artifacts and dependencies
#
# To add project-specific ignores, create additional .gitignore files
# in subdirectories or add them to the end of this file.
#
# Remember to never commit:
# - Database files with real data
# - Environment files with secrets
# - API keys or tokens
# - Build artifacts
# - Dependencies (node_modules, __pycache__)
#
# Always review files before committing with 'git status' and 'git diff'